21-04-1999 - Version 0.1
------------------------

- First (limited) release

22-04-1999 - Version 0.2
------------------------

- Animation is stopped before the popup menu is shown - seems to prevent
  X server crash.
- Some code cleanups.


11-05-1999 - Version 0.3
------------------------

- Always on top option.
- Animation sleeps if the mouse isn't moved for 1 minute.


23-05-1999 - Version 0.4
------------------------

- Session management.
- Vertical offset configurable.
- Real cause of X server crash identified and fixed.

